635
00:31:20,520 --> 00:31:22,680
after the case was solved

636
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:24,600
and he arrested Sun Tan.

637
00:31:24,600 --> 00:31:26,480
Was he targeting the inspectors

638
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:27,640
or Gannandao?

639
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:29,640
Liuniang, you just came back

640
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:31,160
and may not know

641
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,720
