642
00:31:32,720 --> 00:31:35,400
Mingsheng Temple,
where Princess Runing resides,

643
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,720
is often visited

644
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:38,640
by the carriages of Princess of Valor.

645
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:41,880
Princess Runing and Princess Yong'an?

646
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:43,680
His Majesty is young and slow to speak.

647
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:46,240
How much longer can the Empress Dowager
reign over Dacang?

648
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:47,640
Nowadays, many people believe

649
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,320
that the Princess of Valor is more likely

650
00:31:49,320 --> 00:31:51,880
to gain power than Prince Xian.

651
00:31:52,520 --> 00:31:53,920
Has Princess Runing decided

652
00:31:53,920 --> 00:31:55,960
