660
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:09,200
You can even say that

661
00:32:09,200 --> 00:32:10,360
they've stopped the work.

662
00:32:10,360 --> 00:32:11,880
It happened shortly after we returned

663
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:12,920
from Gannandao?

664
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:14,000
Also,

665
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:15,040
Xiang'an has seen

666
00:32:15,040 --> 00:32:17,560
a lot more foreigners
from Nanlang and Xichen recently.

667
00:32:17,560 --> 00:32:18,640
Each thing may seem

668
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:19,960
quite random on its own.

669
00:32:19,960 --> 00:32:22,040
But if you connect them…

670
00:32:22,040 --> 00:32:23,240
Could there be

671
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:24,680
some connections there?

672
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:25,760
Liuniang.

673
00:32:25,760 --> 00:32:27,000
I stand by what I said.

674
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:28,760
So many people in the court

675
00:32:28,760 --> 00:32:30,360
are watching you and your husband.

676
00:32:30,360 --> 00:32:32,160
I bet you know that.

677
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:33,720
I won't blame you if you decide

678
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:35,720
not to help me.

679
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,960
Mr. Xu,

680
00:32:39,960 --> 00:32:41,240
we survived multiple attacks

681
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:43,320
on the way back from Yingzhou

682
00:32:43,320 --> 00:32:46,320
thanks to the help of the inspectors.

683
00:32:46,320 --> 00:32:47,600
If not for this token,

684
00:32:47,600 --> 00:32:49,640
I wouldn't be able to see you today.

685
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:51,720
It's time to return it

686
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:54,120
to its rightful owner.

687
00:32:58,520 --> 00:33:00,680
Liuniang.

688
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:02,840
Sun Tan may not come out
of the Imperial Inspectorate

689
00:33:02,840 --> 00:33:04,800
unscathed.

690
00:33:04,800 --> 00:33:06,400
But if he has been wronged

691
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:07,960
or has something to say,

692
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:11,080
I will surely help him.

693
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:13,240
Can you help me

694
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:15,400
see him?

695
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:19,760
I will draft an application

696
00:33:19,760 --> 00:33:22,280
to be the presiding judge right now.

697
00:33:22,280 --> 00:33:24,880
Sun Tan may be locked up
in the Imperial Inspectorate,

698
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,440
but the presiding judge

699
