714
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:40,712
Only two people are allowed in.

715
00:34:43,239 --> 00:34:46,440
Wait for me at the Ministry of Justice.

716
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:49,840
Then I'll wait for you outside.

717
00:34:51,640 --> 00:34:55,592
[Imperial Inspectorate]

718
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:27,368
Marshal Sun.

719
00:35:28,760 --> 00:35:31,120
Marshal Sun.

720
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:33,160
Marshal Sun.

721
00:35:33,160 --> 00:35:34,160
It's me.

722
00:35:34,160 --> 00:35:36,872
Yan Xing.

723
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:50,040
Have you joined that villain?

724
00:35:50,040 --> 00:35:52,000
I am made the presiding judge.

725
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:54,160
I'm here to do you justice.

726
00:35:54,160 --> 00:35:55,680
The Imperial Inspectorate

727
00:35:55,680 --> 00:35:57,160
accuses you of accepting bribes

728
00:35:57,160 --> 00:35:58,560
and colluding with bandits.

729
00:35:58,560 --> 00:36:00,560
Tell me if you're wronged.

730
00:36:00,560 --> 00:36:01,640
I'll report it.

731
00:36:01,640 --> 00:36:03,912
It's pointless.

732
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:07,920
It's pointless.

733
00:36:14,120 --> 00:36:15,680
If there is injustice,

734
00:36:15,680 --> 00:36:18,120
Marshal Xu and the other inspectors

735
00:36:18,120 --> 00:36:20,000
will risk their lives to rescue you.

736
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:21,200
I will also give it my all

737
00:36:21,200 --> 00:36:23,680
to seek justice for you.

738
00:36:23,680 --> 00:36:26,320
The more you help, the more people die.

739
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,960
Just leave.

740
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:39,336
Sun Tan.

741
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:42,760
I'm not dead yet.

742
00:36:49,600 --> 00:36:52,360
Marshal Xu.

743
00:36:53,120 --> 00:36:54,320
[Marshal of Inspectors]
This token

744
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:55,840
is still waiting for you.

745
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:58,120
Hang in there.

746
00:37:01,284 --> 00:37:03,877
[Marshal of Inspectors]

747
00:37:23,680 --> 00:37:27,520
Director Yan, I have something to say.

748
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:28,520
Okay.

749
00:37:28,520 --> 00:37:30,680
Okay, I'll take notes.

750
00:37:41,080 --> 00:37:44,920
Most of the inspectors
came from all walks of life.

751
00:37:46,160 --> 00:37:49,440
We were all captivated by Marshal Xu's aura

752
00:37:49,440 --> 00:37:52,280
and joined the group as inspectors.

753
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:53,800
In Gannandao,

754
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:56,200
I naturally hoped to build wide connections

755
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:58,720
with the talented as Marshal Xu did.

756
00:37:58,720 --> 00:38:00,920
So-called "collusion with bandits".

757
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:04,240
What about accepting the bribes?

758
00:38:04,240 --> 00:38:06,800
This I can't deny.

759
00:38:07,520 --> 00:38:10,040
I did take money.

760
00:38:10,040 --> 00:38:12,680
Gannandao has many merchants coming and going.

761
00:38:12,680 --> 00:38:13,720
We inspectors

762
