771
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:38,200
Lai Luozhi wants to take out the leader
of the inspectors in Gannandao.

772
00:38:40,160 --> 00:38:41,440
Marshal Sun.

773
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:44,120
