774
00:38:44,120 --> 00:38:46,000
After Mo Qianzhi died,

775
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,720
Lai Luozhi put his people

776
00:38:47,720 --> 00:38:49,840
in Yingzhou as officials.

777
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:51,920
Gannandao is on a key location at the border

778
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:53,680
leading directly to Xichen.

779
00:38:53,680 --> 00:38:55,000
People can even take a detour

780
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:57,760
via Gannandao all the way from Nanlang.

781
00:38:57,760 --> 00:39:00,240
Without the inspectors there,

782
00:39:00,240 --> 00:39:02,560
the border…

783
00:39:03,520 --> 00:39:05,160
Xiang'an has seen

784
00:39:05,160 --> 00:39:08,000
a lot more foreigners from Nanlang and Xichen.

785
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:09,840
It seems Lai Luozhi

786
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:12,200
intends to dominate Gannandao.

787
00:39:12,200 --> 00:39:13,440
But what he's aiming for

788
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:15,000
is far beyond that area.

789
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,920
He's probably plotting with foreign powers

790
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:19,160
to commit treason.

791
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:24,360
Marshal Xu.

792
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:29,040
You'll need evidence even if

793
00:39:29,040 --> 00:39:31,520
you want to frame me.

794
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:37,160
Mrs. Shen.

795
00:39:37,160 --> 00:39:39,760
You came to visit my workplace,

796
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:43,480
