813
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:31,848
How dare you!

814
00:40:33,680 --> 00:40:35,040
Marshal Xu.

815
00:40:35,040 --> 00:40:37,120
Director Yan.

816
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:39,280
Go back.

817
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,720
I don't intend to keep you

818
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:09,800
